British Chambers of Commerce to Run Enterprise Network, FT Says

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-04-06T05:04:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/british-chambers-of-commerce-to-run-enterprise-network-ft-says.html
U.K. Communities Secretary Eric Pickles will announce today that the British Chambers of
Commerce will be the leading partner in a network of local
enterprise partnerships that’s replacing regional development
agencies, the Financial Times reported.  David Frost, the chamber’s director-general, will be the
chairman of the network, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 